lain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">April 25, 2024</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="blog-post" href="/blog-post/opposition-divided-over-history-leading-putin"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_1402326599.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_1402326599.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="Boris Yeltsin in front of a group of reporters in 1991" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Blog post</div><div class="teaser-topic">Post-Cold War</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">Opposition Divided over History Leading to Putin</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">Maxim Trudolyubov</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">April 23, 2024</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="blog-post" href="/blog-post/do-you-have-moment-talk-about-war"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2245768327.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2245768327.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="Christmas tree in front of ruined buildings in Ukraine" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Blog post</div><div class="teaser-topic">Civil Society</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">Do You Have a Moment to Talk about the War?</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">Anna Ryzhkova</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">April 18, 2024</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="blog-post" href="/blog-post/back-future-russias-new-and-old-economic-policy"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2448033165.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2448033165.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="Bank of Russia" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Blog post</div><div class="teaser-topic">Economics and Globalization</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">Back to the Future: Russia’s New (and Old) Economic Policy</span></div><div class="teaser-byline"><div class="teaser-byline-text"><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">By&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-author">William E. Pomeranz</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-plain">&nbsp;on&nbsp;</span><span class="teaser-byline-text-date">April 18, 2024</span></div></div></div></a><a class="teaser" data-type="blog-post" href="/blog-post/sanctions-are-spoiling-russias-plans-make-its-own-airplanes"><div class="teaser-image"><picture><source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2263994289.webp" type="image/webp"/><img src="/sites/default/files/styles/teaser/public/media/uploads/images/shutterstock_2263994289.jpg" width="250" height="160" alt="russia plane manufacturer" loading="lazy"></picture></div><div class="teaser-content"><div class="teaser-top-meta"><div class="teaser-type">Blog post</div><div class="teaser-topic">Economics and Globalization</div></div><div class="teaser-title"><span class="teaser-title-text">Sanctions Are Spoilin